  <description type="morphology">Perennials, 30–90 cm. Internodes (± mid stem) 5–11 cm. Leaves: petioles 0–1 mm; blades simple or 3-foliolate, simple blades or leaflets ± lance-elliptic to narrowly lanceolate, 25–55(–100+) × (4–)6–15(–30+) mm (seldom lobed). Peduncles 2–6+ cm. Calyculi of 7–8 oblong to linear bractlets 3–6 mm. Phyllaries 8, lance-oblong to lance-ovate, 6–8 mm. Ray laminae 12–30+ mm. Disc florets 40–80+; corollas yellow (often drying blackish to purplish), 6–7 mm. Cypselae obovate to oblong, 4–5 mm. 2n = 26, 78, 104.</description>
  <description type="phenology">Flowering May–Aug.</description>
